}

{
  "prompt": "A toy action figure of a smiling man with long curly black hair and a beard, wearing a navy blue polo shirt and black pants, inside a collectible clear plastic display box with a cardboard backing. The accessories in the box include a tiny microphone headset, a coffee cup with Arabic calligraphy, a miniature book titled 'Baraka Economics', a laptop with code on the screen, a sourdough loaf, and a tiny plush version of a toddler named Suleiman wearing a cozy scarf. The background inside the box shows a cozy creative workspace with plants, books, and spiritual symbols.",
