{
  "prompt": "A stylized toy action figure of a smiling man with long curly black hair and a beard, dressed in a navy polo shirt and black pants. The figure is presented in clear toy packaging with a gradient background. He appears more toy-like with a shiny, smooth plastic appearance and simplified facial features. The box includes accessories such as a miniature microphone, a rolled-up scroll representing a thesis, a tiny coffee brewing set, a laptop with stickers, a tiny illustrated book titled 'Barakanomics,' and a small toy figure of a toddler wearing overalls named Suleiman. The packaging style is playful, designed like a collectible figure.",
