  "prompt": "Two cute, cartoon-style kiwi fruits with soft brown skin and golden yellow interiors, standing upright and leaning toward each other as if kissing. They have expressive little eyes and tiny blush marks, surrounded by soft hearts and sparkles in a warm beige background. The scene is whimsical and innocent, evoking affection and sweetness.",
