{
  "prompt": "Three flyer design variations for a warm kindness-themed WhatsApp invitation. Each flyer includes space for a QR code and features a cartoon kiwi bird holding a golden kiwi fruit. Style 1 is poetic and soft, with the phrase 'Be a Kindness Kiwi'; Style 2 is minimalist and calm, with the phrase 'Small Acts, Golden Seeds'; Style 3 is playful and community-oriented, with the phrase 'Join the Kindness Garden'. All are set on beige or soft earth-tone backgrounds with friendly typography and inviting visuals.",
